<graph edgedefault="undirected"><node id="Stanford Type B Aortic Dissection (TBAD)">
  <data key="d0">Stanford Type B Aortic Dissection (TBAD)</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">TBAD is a life-threatening vascular disease with high mortality, characterized by acute onset and rapid progression. It involves an intimal tear allowing blood to enter the aortic wall, creating true and false lumens.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8bd659a5f64c634b63d799dfc186f28b</data>
  <data key="d4">Stanford+B+型主动脉夹层诊断和治疗中国专家共识（2022版）.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1779836582</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Chinese Medical Association Surgical Branch Vascular Surgery Group">
  <data key="d0">Chinese Medical Association Surgical Branch Vascular Surgery Group</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">This group authored the 2022 Chinese expert consensus and the 2008 guideline on endovascular treatment for aortic dissection.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8bd659a5f64c634b63d799dfc186f28b</data>
  <data key="d4">Stanford+B+型主动脉夹层诊断和治疗中国专家共识（2022版）.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1779836582</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="2022 Chinese Expert Consensus on Diagnosis and Treatment of Stanford Type B Aortic Dissection">
  <data key="d0">2022 Chinese Expert Consensus on Diagnosis and Treatment of Stanford Type B Aortic Dissection</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">A consensus document providing principles and guidance for TBAD diagnosis and treatment, incorporating new endovascular techniques and evidence.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8bd659a5f64c634b63d799dfc186f28b</data>
  <data key="d4">Stanford+B+型主动脉夹层诊断和治疗中国专家共识（2022版）.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1779836582</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="DeBakey Classification">
  <data key="d0">DeBakey Classification</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Introduced in 1965, this classification divides aortic dissection into type I, II, and III based on primary tear location and extent.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8bd659a5f64c634b63d799dfc186f28b</data>
  <data key="d4">Stanford+B+型主动脉夹层诊断和治疗中国专家共识（2022版）.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1779836582</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Stanford Classification">
  <data key="d0">Stanford Classification</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Proposed in 1970 by Daily et al., this simplified classification divides aortic dissection into type A (involving ascending aorta) and type B (not involving ascending aorta).</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8bd659a5f64c634b63d799dfc186f28b</data>
  <data key="d4">Stanford+B+型主动脉夹层诊断和治疗中国专家共识（2022版）.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1779836582</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Non-A Non-B Aortic Dissection">
  <data key="d0">Non-A Non-B Aortic Dissection</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">A new concept where the primary tear is in the arch or type B dissection extends proximally into the arch, supplementing the Stanford classification.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8bd659a5f64c634b63d799dfc186f28b</data>
  <data key="d4">Stanford+B+型主动脉夹层诊断和治疗中国专家共识（2022版）.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1779836582</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Society for Vascular Surgery (SVS)">
  <data key="d0">Society for Vascular Surgery (SVS)</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">An American society that co-published the new anatomic classification of aortic dissection.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8bd659a5f64c634b63d799dfc186f28b</data>
  <data key="d4">Stanford+B+型主动脉夹层诊断和治疗中国专家共识（2022版）.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1779836582</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Society of Thoracic Surgeons (STS)">
  <data key="d0">Society of Thoracic Surgeons (STS)</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">An American society that collaborated with SVS on the anatomic classification.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8bd659a5f64c634b63d799dfc186f28b</data>
  <data key="d4">Stanford+B+型主动脉夹层诊断和治疗中国专家共识（2022版）.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1779836582</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="SVS/STS Anatomic Classification">
  <data key="d0">SVS/STS Anatomic Classification</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">A detailed zone-based classification (zones 0-8) of aortic dissection anatomy, published by SVS and STS.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8bd659a5f64c634b63d799dfc186f28b</data>
  <data key="d4">Stanford+B+型主动脉夹层诊断和治疗中国专家共识（2022版）.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1779836582</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Endovascular Repair">
  <data key="d0">Endovascular Repair</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">A minimally invasive technique for aortic dissection, first performed for TBAD in 1996, which significantly lowered perioperative mortality and complications.&lt;SEP&gt;Endovascular repair is a treatment method for TBAD, including reintervention for complications like severe endoleak or stent infection.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8bd659a5f64c634b63d799dfc186f28b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4c6c2b152c9eaada554199a5037bc57d</data>
  <data key="d4">Stanford+B+型主动脉夹层诊断和治疗中国专家共识（2022版）.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1779836582</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="2008 Guideline on Endovascular Treatment of Aortic Dissection">
  <data key="d0">2008 Guideline on Endovascular Treatment of Aortic Dissection</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Earlier guidelines issued by the Chinese Medical Association Vascular Surgery Group, providing recommendations on etiology, diagnosis, and endovascular therapy.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8bd659a5f64c634b63d799dfc186f28b</data>
  <data key="d4">Stanford+B+型主动脉夹层诊断和治疗中国专家共识（2022版）.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1779836582</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Stock Markets">
  <data key="d0">Stock Markets</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Stock markets faced a sharp downturn today, reflecting the overall decline in financial trading.&lt;SEP&gt;Stock markets faced a sharp downturn today, reflecting overall declines in stock values.&lt;SEP&gt;Stock markets faced a sharp downturn today, largely driven by declines in tech giants.&lt;SEP&gt;Stock markets faced a sharp downturn today, reflecting the overall decline in stock values.&lt;SEP&gt;Stock markets faced a sharp downturn today due to declines in tech giants and investor concerns.&lt;SEP&gt;Stock markets faced a sharp downturn today, reflecting overall declines in stock values.&lt;SEP&gt;Stock markets faced a sharp downturn today, reflecting the overall decline in stock values.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8bd659a5f64c634b63d799dfc186f28b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-64e4ac484241fa2935c4cb7924488a0b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-605ec9a012188bcab7dd557b160b0311&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4c6c2b152c9eaada554199a5037bc57d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e562c0cde0c973324835a564611458a5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-591716ddeca1a26bf837c5b70ca9d6db&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b85f53c31ce42d37f83b5008e14bf203&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-09381648ecd5917039e244d62da638ee&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-61317a57efdf6bb9fc1bcf3ec62ff924</data>
