  <data key="d5">1779837098</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Tech Giants">
  <data key="d0">Tech Giants</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Tech giants are major technology companies that saw significant declines in their stock values.&lt;SEP&gt;Tech giants are major technology companies that saw significant declines, contributing to the drop in the global tech index.&lt;SEP&gt;Tech giants saw significant declines, contributing to the drop in the global tech index.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8bd659a5f64c634b63d799dfc186f28b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-64e4ac484241fa2935c4cb7924488a0b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-605ec9a012188bcab7dd557b160b0311&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4c6c2b152c9eaada554199a5037bc57d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e562c0cde0c973324835a564611458a5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-09381648ecd5917039e244d62da638ee</data>
  <data key="d4">Stanford+B+型主动脉夹层诊断和治疗中国专家共识（2022版）.pdf&lt;SEP&gt;子宫内膜异位症超声评估中国专家共识.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1779837098</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Analysts">
  <data key="d0">Analysts</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Analysts attribute the market selloff to investor concerns over rising interest rates and regulatory uncertainty.&lt;SEP&gt;Analysts attribute the stock market selloff to investor concerns over rising interest rates and regulatory uncertainty.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8bd659a5f64c634b63d799dfc186f28b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-64e4ac484241fa2935c4cb7924488a0b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4c6c2b152c9eaada554199a5037bc57d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e562c0cde0c973324835a564611458a5</data>
  <data key="d4">Stanford+B+型主动脉夹层诊断和治疗中国专家共识（2022版）.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1779836582</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Investor Concerns">
  <data key="d0">Investor Concerns</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Investor concerns over rising interest rates and regulatory uncertainty are the cause of the market selloff.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8bd659a5f64c634b63d799dfc186f28b</data>
  <data key="d4">Stanford+B+型主动脉夹层诊断和治疗中国专家共识（2022版）.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1779836582</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Rising Interest Rates">
  <data key="d0">Rising Interest Rates</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Rising interest rates are identified as a macroeconomic factor that causes investor concern and contributes to market selloffs. As a broader economic force, rising interest rates create apprehension among investors, which subsequently acts as a catalyst for selling off market assets. This dynamic highlights the significant impact that upward movements in interest rates have on market behavior and investor sentiment.&lt;SEP&gt;Rising interest rates are a concern for investors, contributing to the market selloff.&lt;SEP&gt;Rising interest rates are a factor causing investor concerns and contributing to the market selloff.&lt;SEP&gt;Rising interest rates are a macroeconomic factor causing investor concerns and contributing to the market selloff.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8bd659a5f64c634b63d799dfc186f28b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-64e4ac484241fa2935c4cb7924488a0b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-605ec9a012188bcab7dd557b160b0311&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4c6c2b152c9eaada554199a5037bc57d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1cfaf9e1c9e4a4c49d23e85f0cbdc90c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e562c0cde0c973324835a564611458a5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-591716ddeca1a26bf837c5b70ca9d6db&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-06febe8127a0fccc661f447996c2a367&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-94e6c2d3a322064c0bedf6b639e576b4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ecea5c0d8fe77f18274ef9e323deab43&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b85f53c31ce42d37f83b5008e14bf203&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-09381648ecd5917039e244d62da638ee&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-61317a57efdf6bb9fc1bcf3ec62ff924&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8cbe0f288d4aaea04ac19b92c24f1266&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0dd3aace07e5e2f67f60579de0b36b76</data>
  <data key="d4">Stanford+B+型主动脉夹层诊断和治疗中国专家共识（2022版）.pdf&lt;SEP&gt;mineru_todo1992.pdf&lt;SEP&gt;shchelochkov2019.pdf&lt;SEP&gt;子宫内膜异位症超声评估中国专家共识.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1779837098</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Regulatory Uncertainty">
  <data key="d0">Regulatory Uncertainty</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Regulatory uncertainty is a condition or factor that causes investor concern and contributes to market selloffs. It is frequently cited as a significant driver of investor apprehension, which in turn prompts or exacerbates broader market sell-offs. Specifically within the tech sector, regulatory uncertainty acts as a notable catalyst for investor concern, directly contributing to downward market pressures and selloffs in that industry.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8bd659a5f64c634b63d799dfc186f28b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-64e4ac484241fa2935c4cb7924488a0b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-605ec9a012188bcab7dd557b160b0311&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4c6c2b152c9eaada554199a5037bc57d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1cfaf9e1c9e4a4c49d23e85f0cbdc90c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e562c0cde0c973324835a564611458a5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-591716ddeca1a26bf837c5b70ca9d6db&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-06febe8127a0fccc661f447996c2a367&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-94e6c2d3a322064c0bedf6b639e576b4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ecea5c0d8fe77f18274ef9e323deab43&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b85f53c31ce42d37f83b5008e14bf203&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-09381648ecd5917039e244d62da638ee&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-61317a57efdf6bb9fc1bcf3ec62ff924&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8cbe0f288d4aaea04ac19b92c24f1266&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0dd3aace07e5e2f67f60579de0b36b76</data>
  <data key="d4">Stanford+B+型主动脉夹层诊断和治疗中国专家共识（2022版）.pdf&lt;SEP&gt;mineru_todo1992.pdf&lt;SEP&gt;shchelochkov2019.pdf&lt;SEP&gt;子宫内膜异位症超声评估中国专家共识.pdf</data>
  <data key="d5">1779837125</data>
