</node>
<node id="Commodity Markets">
  <data key="d0">Commodity Markets</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Commodity markets reflected a mixed sentiment, with gold futures rising and crude oil prices rallying.&lt;SEP&gt;Commodity markets reflected mixed sentiment with gold futures rising and crude oil prices rallying.&lt;SEP&gt;Commodity markets reflected a mixed sentiment with gold and crude oil prices rising.</data>
