</node>
<node id="Federal Reserve">
  <data key="d0">Federal Reserve</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">The Federal Reserve is the central banking system whose upcoming policy moves and potential rate hikes are being closely watched by financial experts.&lt;SEP&gt;The Federal Reserve is the central banking system whose upcoming policy announcement and potential rate hikes are highly anticipated by financial experts.&lt;SEP&gt;The Federal Reserve is the central banking system whose upcoming policy moves and potential rate hikes are being closely watched by financial experts.&lt;SEP&gt;The Federal Reserve is the central banking system whose upcoming policy moves are being closely watched by financial experts.&lt;SEP&gt;The Federal Reserve is the central banking system whose upcoming policy moves and potential rate hikes are being closely watched by financial experts.&lt;SEP&gt;The Federal Reserve is the central banking system whose upcoming policy moves are being closely watched by financial experts.&lt;SEP&gt;The Federal Reserve is the central banking system whose upcoming policy moves and potential rate hikes are being closely watched by financial experts.</data>
