  <data key="d2">Cruz is associated with a vision of control and order, influencing the dynamics among other characters.&lt;SEP&gt;Cruz is associated with a vision of control and order, influencing the dynamics among other characters.&lt;SEP&gt;Cruz is associated with a vision of control and order, influencing the dynamics among other characters.&lt;SEP&gt;Cruz is a character associated with a narrowing vision of control and order, which contrasts with the shared commitment to discovery held by Alex and Jordan.&lt;SEP&gt;Cruz is associated with a vision of control and order, influencing the dynamics among other characters.&lt;SEP&gt;Cruz is associated with a vision of control and order, influencing the dynamics among other characters.&lt;SEP&gt;Cruz is associated with a vision of control and order, influencing the dynamics among other characters.</data>
