  <data key="d0">The Device</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">The Device is central to the story, with potential game-changing implications, and is revered by Taylor.&lt;SEP&gt;The Device is central to the story, with potential game-changing implications, and is revered by Taylor.&lt;SEP&gt;The Device is central to the story, with potential game-changing implications, and is revered by Taylor.&lt;SEP&gt;The Device is a piece of technology observed by Taylor and Jordan, possessing potential game-changing implications if understood.&lt;SEP&gt;The Device is central to the story, with potential game-changing implications, and is revered by Taylor.&lt;SEP&gt;The Device is central to the story, with potential game-changing implications, and is revered by Taylor.&lt;SEP&gt;The Device is central to the story, with potential game-changing implications, and is revered by Taylor.</data>
