<node id="MDT Cooperation">
  <data key="d0">MDT Cooperation</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">MDT (Multidisciplinary Team) cooperation is recommended during surgery for paraplegia high-risk patients.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-591716ddeca1a26bf837c5b70ca9d6db</data>
  <data key="d4">Stanford+B+型主动脉夹层诊断和治疗中国专家共识（2022版）.pdf</data>
