  <data key="d0">University of Pittsburgh</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">The University of Pittsburgh is the medical facility where Patient 2 was flown for OLT due to deterioration and stage III and IV coma.&lt;SEP&gt;The University of Pittsburgh is an academic institution associated with the authors' Department of Surgery.&lt;SEP&gt;University of Pittsburgh is a university in Pittsburgh, Pennsylvania, associated with the Department of Surgery.&lt;SEP&gt;A medical institution where Patient 2 was flown for OLT after his condition deteriorated into stage III and IV coma.</data>
