  <data key="d2">Kagoshima University is the institution where liver tissues from Patient 2 were analyzed for CPS-I, OTC, ASS, and AS activity.&lt;SEP&gt;Kagoshima University in Japan is the institution where Takeyori Saheki works in the Department of Biochemistry.&lt;SEP&gt;An institution whose Department of Biochemistry analyzed CPS-I, OTC, ASS, and AS activity in Patient 2's liver tissues.</data>
