  <data key="d0">CPS-I Deficiency</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">A urea cycle enzyme deficiency characterized by undetectable CPS-I activity in the liver, leading to hyperammonemia and plasma amino acid abnormalities.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-d261ff81dd6e7861a19f6ec0e7ba683d</data>
