  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">The organization that organized domestic experts to form the consensus on sonographic evaluation of endometriosis.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-09381648ecd5917039e244d62da638ee</data>
  <data key="d4">子宫内膜异位症超声评估中国专家共识.pdf</data>
