  <data key="d2">A corresponding author of the Chinese expert consensus on sonographic evaluation of endometriosis.&lt;SEP&gt;Tian Jiawei is the head of the Consensus Writing Group and a core expert from The Second Affiliated Hospital of Harbin Medical University.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-09381648ecd5917039e244d62da638ee&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8cbe0f288d4aaea04ac19b92c24f1266</data>
