  <data key="d0">Peking Union Medical College Hospital</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Peking Union Medical College Hospital is a medical institution affiliated with the Chinese Academy of Medical Sciences and Peking Union Medical College.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8cbe0f288d4aaea04ac19b92c24f1266</data>
  <data key="d4">子宫内膜异位症超声评估中国专家共识.pdf</data>
