  <data key="d2">The First Affiliated Hospital of Sun Yat-sen University is a medical institution where Xie Hongning works.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8cbe0f288d4aaea04ac19b92c24f1266</data>
  <data key="d4">子宫内膜异位症超声评估中国专家共识.pdf</data>
